717835f-a.title: Manhattan: Broadway - 228th Street (West)
717835f-a.text:
Broadway, west side, north from West 228th Street, and showing the
wist side I.R.T. subway line, running northward thereon and to the Borough
of the Bronx. The workers shown,are at the S.W. corner of the first
Nmentioned point, at which location a new apartment is being constructed.
The 1-story garages are at the N.W. corner of same.
October 27, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
